msgid "# Quickstart"
msgstr "# 快速开始"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"This section guides you through container-based environment setup and large "
"model inference, using the Qwen3-0.6B offline single-GPU inference script as"
" an example."
msgstr "本节将指导您完成基于容器的环境搭建和大模型推理，以 Qwen3-0.6B 离线单卡推理脚本为例。"

msgid ""
"- For details on using different models, see the corresponding model tutorial in the \"Model Tutorials\" directory, for example, [Qwen3-30B-A3B](tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md).\n"
"- For details on using different functions, see the corresponding function tutorial in the \"Function Tutorials\" directory, for example, [Prefill-Decode Disaggregation (Deepseek)](tutorials/features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"- 关于使用不同模型的详细信息，请参见“模型教程”目录下的对应模型教程，例如 [Qwen3-30B-A3B](tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md)。\n"
"- 关于使用不同功能的详细信息，请参见“功能教程”目录下的对应功能教程，例如 [Prefill-Decode 分离部署 (Deepseek)](tutorials/features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid "## Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 前提条件"

msgid "### Supported Devices"
msgstr "### 支持的设备"

msgid ""
"- Atlas A2 training series (Atlas 800T A2, Atlas 900 A2 PoD, Atlas 200T A2 Box16, Atlas 300T A2)\n"
"- Atlas 800I A2 inference series (Atlas 800I A2)\n"
"- Atlas A3 training series (Atlas 800T A3, Atlas 900 A3 SuperPoD, Atlas 9000 A3 SuperPoD)\n"
"- Atlas 800I A3 inference series (Atlas 800I A3)\n"
"- [Experimental] Atlas 300I inference series (Atlas 300I Duo)"
msgstr ""
"- Atlas A2 训练系列（Atlas 800T A2、Atlas 900 A2 PoD、Atlas 200T A2 Box16、Atlas 300T A2）\n"
"- Atlas 800I A2 推理系列（Atlas 800I A2）\n"
"- Atlas A3 训练系列（Atlas 800T A3、Atlas 900 A3 SuperPoD、Atlas 9000 A3 SuperPoD）\n"
"- Atlas 800I A3 推理系列（Atlas 800I A3）\n"
"- [实验性] Atlas 300I 推理系列（Atlas 300I Duo）"

msgid "## Requirements"
msgstr "## 环境要求"

msgid ""
"- OS: Linux\n"
"- Python: >= 3.10, < 3.13\n"
"- Hardware with Ascend NPUs. It's usually the Atlas 800 A2 series.\n"
"- Software:"
msgstr ""
"- 操作系统：Linux\n"
"- Python：>= 3.10, < 3.13\n"
"- 硬件：配备昇腾 NPU，通常为 Atlas 800 A2 系列。\n"
"- 软件："

msgid "## Setup environment using container"
msgstr "## 使用容器搭建环境"

msgid ""
"Before using containers, make sure Docker is installed on your system. If "
"Docker is not installed, please refer to the [Docker installation "
"guide](https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/) for installation instructions."
msgstr ""
"在使用容器之前，请确保您的系统已安装 Docker。如果尚未安装 Docker，请参考 [Docker "
"安装指南](https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/) 进行安装。"

msgid "=== \"Ubuntu\""
msgstr "=== \"Ubuntu\""

msgid "=== \"openEuler\""
msgstr "=== \"openEuler\""

msgid ""
"The default workdir is `/workspace`, vLLM and vLLM Ascend code are placed in"
" `/vllm-workspace` and installed in [development "
"mode](https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide/development_mode.html) "
"(`pip install -e`) to help developers make changes effective immediately "
"without requiring a new installation."
msgstr ""
"默认工作目录为 `/workspace`，vLLM 和 vLLM Ascend 代码放置在 `/vllm-workspace` "
"中，并以[开发模式](https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide/development_mode.html)（`pip"
" install -e`）安装，以便开发者修改后立即生效，无需重新安装。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使用方法"

msgid "You can use ModelScope mirror to speed up download:"
msgstr "您可以使用 ModelScope 镜像加速下载："

msgid "There are two ways to start vLLM on Ascend NPU:"
msgstr "在昇腾 NPU 上启动 vLLM 有两种方式："

msgid "=== \"Offline Batched Inference\""
msgstr "=== \"离线批量推理\""

msgid ""
"With vLLM installed, you can start generating texts for list of input "
"prompts (i.e. offline batch inference)."
msgstr "安装 vLLM 后，您可以开始为输入提示列表生成文本（即离线批量推理）。"

msgid "Create and run a simple inference test. The `example.py` can be like:"
msgstr "创建并运行一个简单的推理测试。`example.py` 的内容可以如下："

msgid "Then run:"
